{"_id":"28ee4e3e6061e1320d552f6220a8c52d","chapter":"1","section":"1","title":"微分方程的基本概念","_openid":"ofw784r8wjzd-wj2zE823LJpQlOo","lighted_num":"1","lights":"1","content":"<h3>微分方程</h3><p>定义:自变量只有一个的微分方程为常微分方程</p><h3>阶</h3><p>定义:微分方程未知函数的最高阶导数或微分的阶数</p><p>一般形式：<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/1.1.png?sign=5f0cb4d7632d4032596b2e2c785f6217&t=1621144845\" alt=\"\" /></p><h3>线性与非线性</h3><p>定义:若方程<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/1.2.png?sign=ba54ef780809ad72c0d7cacbd4daf885&t=1621144866\" />为y,<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/1.3.png?sign=8d1d44a84917cd306c48724c3683f282&t=1621144880\"/>的一次有理式，则其为n阶线性方程 </p><p>一般形式：<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/1.4.png?sign=22c5fbe7619aa1dd66138582b787911d&t=1621144900\"/></p>"}
{"_id":"79550af260a0b7f3173c9cff4129b16d","chapter":"1","section":"2","title":"微分方程的解和几何解释","_openid":"ofw784r8wjzd-wj2zE823LJpQlOo","lighted_num":"1","lights":"1","content":"<h3>解</h3><p>定义:</p><p>y=φ(x)在I上有直到n阶的连续导数 </p><p>y=φ(x)为方程在<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/1.2.png?sign=31090caf54c3013c489366d9070aa379&t=1621145796\"/>在I上的一个解</p><p>显式/隐式解：</p><p>隐式：最终解的形式为隐函数</p><p>显式：如解的定义中所描述的形式</p><p>通/特解：</p><p>通解：解中含有相互独立的任意常数，且其常数个数与微分方程的阶数相同。形如<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/1.5.png?sign=a22c1d1b211101a955bd8896387ab432&t=1621145829\"/></p><p>特解：给定常数确定值得到的解</p><p>定解条件：实际问题附加给微分方程的条件，求解该类问题为定解问题</p><p>初始条件（初值问题）：x=x0时y=y0，<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/1.7.png?sign=3ae224324258676b1ffd200ad3b463af&t=1621145837\"/></p><p>驻定方程：<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/1.8.png?sign=b26f02f0e9d98ec45b750930d1e1ebe1&t=1621145848\"/>，即右侧不含自变量t，则方程驻定/自治。</p><p>相空间：不含自变量，仅含有未知函数组成的空间，积分曲线在相空间的投影为轨线</p><p><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/1.9.png?sign=3b0e5d56288a2d0bb5b79aea1fc73182&t=1621145859\"/>该解也称为平衡解、驻定解或奇点、平衡点。</p>\n"}
{"_id":"79550af260a0b963173d078a09beab89","chapter":"2","section":"1","title":"变量分离方程与变量分离法","_openid":"ofw784r8wjzd-wj2zE823LJpQlOo","lighted_num":"1","lights":"1","content":"<h3>变量分离方程</h3><ul><li>形如 <img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.1.png?sign=313431f96da8de2b0bd105961f369930&t=1621146542\" alt=\"\"/>的方程，称为变量分离方程</li></ul><h3>齐次方程</h3><ul><li>形如 <img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.2.png?sign=e9073111b1e30f4c4f0faacd79bc8647&t=1621146573\" alt=\"\"/>的方程，称为齐次方程</li></ul>\n"}
{"_id":"28ee4e3e60a26276199427df1bdf0ccd","chapter":"2","section":"2","title":"一阶微分方程的初等积分法","_openid":"ofw784r8wjzd-wj2zE823LJpQlOo","lighted_num":"1","lights":"1","content":"<h3>线性微分方程</h3><ul><li>形如 <img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.3.png?sign=1c1cd9d4e2ee9cb254ce4a2ff9232b77&t=1621254369\" />的方程，称为一阶线性方程</li><li>公式<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.4.png?sign=aa81f1cbd1436ed3c142671ccdfe10a4&t=1621254399\" />为一阶线性方程的求解公式</li><li>解法<ul><li>积分因子法</li><li>常数变易法</li></ul> </li> <li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.5.png?sign=3fdf3fccd94763a3a7369a70cce91f24&t=1621254432\">称为伯努利方程</li><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.6.png?sign=8082d05d0751c42ebcb3fbffcde89c84&t=1621254441\">称为黎卡提方程</li></ul>\n"}
{"_id":"79550af260a274c017997cbb1aeaa26f","chapter":"2","section":"3","title":"恰当方程与积分因子法","_openid":"ofw784r8wjzd-wj2zE823LJpQlOo","lighted_num":"1","lights":"1","content":"<h3>恰当方程与积分因子</h3><ul><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.7.png?sign=a2c5ac9d93eee7e076adc7147993e8ac&t=1621259240\">为恰当方程或全微分方程</li><li>恰当的充要条件：<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.8.png?sign=bb322fec401e9766bdf71289c9170f43&t=1621259249\" alt=\"\"></li><li>解法：<ul><li>直接积分</li><li>分组凑微分</li><li>线积分</li></ul></li><li>积分因子：存在<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.9.png?sign=b10a76308ed087dad9d5e3a54f2aa301&t=1621259263\"/>,使得<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.10.png?sign=5a4fe6987a93e6ce59f51bf9f8e441bf&t=1621259282\" alt=\"\">为恰当方程，即对非恰当方程乘以一个积分因子μ(x,y)使之成为恰当方程。</li><li>积分因子充要条件及其求得：<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.11.png?sign=79cb5f24206161a11d6d24ebbc72802a&t=1621259296\" alt=\"\"></li><li>两个积分因子都可以通过定义来计算，但这样比较繁琐。<ul><li>尝试计算ψ及φ，看看是否真的与x，y无关，并求解。</li><li>若能猜测积分因子的基本形式，可进行假设，然后根据恰当方程的定义求解。</li><li>试图直接找出原本微分方程的全微分形式，并加以求解。</li></ul></li></ul>\n"}
{"_id":"cbddf0af60a274d3093762ac4faed450","chapter":"2","section":"4","title":"一阶隐式方程与引入参数法","_openid":"ofw784r8wjzd-wj2zE823LJpQlOo","lighted_num":"1","lights":"1","content":"<h3>一阶隐式方程及参数表示</h3><ul><li>一般形式：<img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.12.png?sign=f62c2e9fb6f41c45287a4548ecbd90d6&t=1621259583\"/>，引入参数，转化为可解类型</li><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.13.png?sign=7ddbe2802090d61d09b0527665148b5f&t=1621259597\"/><ul><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.14.png?sign=d141012b1c1f38c1ba29129fffee2ec1&t=1621259609\" alt=\"\"></li><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.15.png?sign=2c6acbb9ba31cb857115beb7de020499&t=1621259618\"/></li></ul></li><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.16.png?sign=b808adc5c5ac501081369694d6a1f87c&t=1621259629\"/><ul><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.17.png?sign=6d87c556adb02930ef674f447b36117a&t=1621259638\" alt=\"\"></li></ul></li><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.18.png?sign=7d54fcfedd0271e2c8668501cf8802d1&t=1621259647\"/><ul><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.19.png?sign=a9c5d3621d4c0573c1cc3b6e73424685&t=1621259658\" alt=\"\"></li></ul></li><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.20.png?sign=2371d09eaac42e63cbbfb94863c867fa&t=1621259673\"/><ul><li><img src=\"https://7973-ysx0827-plc6r-1301864888.tcb.qcloud.la/sections/2.21.png?sign=b1de2e54bf9cbdc05a136c96eade52fa&t=1621259681\" alt=\"\"></li></ul></li> </ul>\n"}
